## Introduction
`IrisAnalysis` provides tools to analyze the `iris` dataset.

## Setup
Install with:
```r
devtools::install_github("jnguyen529/IrisAnalysis")
library(IrisAnalysis)
OR you can simply use the built in "iris" dataset in Rstudio
```

## Examples
### Calculate Means
```r
means <- calc_iris_means()
print(means)
```

### Plot Measurements
```r
plot_iris()
```

### Summarize Measurements
```r
summary <- summarize_iris()
print(summary)
```
